items.title: Apple hikes the cost of a monthly Apple TV+ subscription
items.description: Apple's move to raise the cost of its streaming platform follows similar moves by Netflix and Peacock.

items.title: Woman charged with murder after using abortion pill details claims against D.A.
items.description: Lizelle Gonzalez was indicted on murder charges in 2022, after she used medication to induce an abortion. The charges were later dropped.

items.title: Almost half of adults say they are ordering kids' meals. Here's why.
items.description: Adult customers admit to ordering from kids' menus to save money and eat smaller portions, a new survey shows.

items.title: Data centers face staffing crisis as demand soars for trade workers
items.description: With roughly 400,000 trade jobs unfilled in the U.S., data centers powering the AI boom face a staffing crisis.

items.title: WNBA breaks single-season attendance record
items.description: The Women's National Basketball Association announced it broke its record for attendance during a single season, attracting more than 2.5 million fans...
